// The Space's Overview folded into Home (`/`, SpaceHomeView). This route now just
// redirects so old bookmarks / handoff links don't 404. The setup/edit flow still
// lives at /integrations/configure (a focused sub-flow reached from Home).
// Note: a redirect drops the query string — the live flows link straight to
// `/?status=running` / `/?broken=src` etc., this is only the bare-path safety net.
return Astro.redirect('/');
